description:
For the full recipe: http://www.astigvegan.com/vegan-kaldereta

Kaldereta is a spicy Filipino stew made of hearty ingredients cooked in rich, spicy sauce. The vegan version is just as comforting yet faster and easier to make than the meat version.  Kain na, let's eat!

chapters.title: RED POTATOES 3 PEELED, CUT INTO BIG CHUNKS
